snippet.title: Kowi Ishto Battle of Akonoli - Trailer
snippet.description:
Kowi Ishto: Battle of Akonoli is a 16-bit inspired, Action Packed, Arcade Style, Space Shooter.

Steam Page at:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1224720/Kowi_Ishto_Battle_of_Akonoli
